title: How to add unicode, I have missing Javanese unicode after android 11 update
content: In Android 10, I can pick Javanese (Aksara Jawa) language, after Android 11 update somehow Javanese unicode is missing and I cant see anything related to "Aksara Jawa". Javanese (Aksara Jawa) is also missing on my gboard. Is there anyway to solve this?
